Class MrTreeMap<K,V>

  • java.lang.Object
    • mr.robotto.collections.MrTreeMap<K,V>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Iterable<V>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    MrSceneTreeData

    public class MrTreeMap<K,V>
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Iterable<V>
    Tree Structure. This tree can saves nodes in a hierarchically way. Moreover finding an element is done in O(1) because all ellements are hashed using a MrMapFuncion
